<h2>The legal bit</h2>
<p>Telegraph Media Group Limited’s Introductory Trial Offer gives you access to the Telegraph’s Premium All Digital Access Subscription for a trial period of two months free of charge. You can cancel at any time.         </p>
<p>Your trial subscription will be activated as soon as you have completed your registration and submit your payment details. The Telegraph shall not take payment for the first two months of the introductory trial period. <b>On completion of the trial period you will automatically be charged the full Telegraph Premium subscription fee of £26 a month, unless you cancel beforehand.</b> </p>
<p>Telegraph Media Group Limited reserves the right to hold, void, cancel, suspend, or amend the offer where it becomes necessary to do so. By accepting this offer, you are deemed to have accepted and agreed to be bound by these terms and conditions. This promotion will be governed by English law and subject to the jurisdiction of the English courts.         </p>
